{"tid":687043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【旺角殺街】公民黨倡保留 設分類表演區Mr. Wally周日撐場","createTime":"2018-06-02T00:58:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T02:39:23.000Z","uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e2bb913bd8d755a4697c86e5c99e53366b4d1d06","tid":687043,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T00:58:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180601/58265393\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180601%2F58265393&d=RNTYwoD92dtDUkm2%2B7mGEpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=de527a9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180601%2F58265393&h=0fdab69b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180601/58265393</a>"},{"pid":"f4ebaf55af6644760af13edbea7bc597b6df435f","tid":687043,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T01:01:25.000Z","msg":"（李潤芳攝）(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（李潤芳攝）(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（李潤芳攝）(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（李潤芳攝）(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n旺角行人專區在缺乏管理下，噪音、管理問題形成擾民亂象。油尖旺區區議會上周在保皇黨護航下，通過由經民聯提出的取消行人專區動議。惟公民黨指政府應進行規管運作，而非一刀切抹殺表演者空間，將於星期日在旺角行人專區試行規管，以逼使政府研究推行。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨發起的模擬規管街頭表演，將於星期日（6月3日）下午5時至8時，在介乎豉油街和登打士街的西洋菜南街旺角行人專用區進行。試驗區域設有3個表演圈，當中兩個為音樂表演單位，一個為動態表演單位。每輪音樂表演為1小時，動態表演則每輪30分鐘。並設有緩衝地帶，避免受鄰近聲浪干擾。<br />\n<br />\n他們又參考西九的發牌制度制定管制規則，如表演用品可在三分鐘內移走、禁止使用發電機或大型音響設備和兩米範圍內不高於85分貝。而表演者演出後須重新排隊，才可在同一位置再表演。<br />\n<br />\n現時有8個表演團體或單位答應參與，包括日籍唱作歌手 Mr. Wally、資深街頭藝人「Mr. Funny」蘇春就等，明日亦會進一步與旺角行人專區的其他表演者聯絡，呼籲他們參與。"},{"pid":"427c7935eedfa329ef138dfa1cc5b5df2c096f84","tid":687043,"uid":65530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T01:03:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db8a87c9b1ce30e3bd17b85bc5eedca4cbfaef24","tid":687043,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T01:05:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"05e9a8dc902c32ca95513549c34f1d8d5d211e42","tid":687043,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T01:07:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/090720_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F090720_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2c3fe924&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59e3c5cbc1cd31398f61634790dd719c22a49dd7","tid":687043,"uid":43146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T01:08:49.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"2c9680110dbe52d2e33d5fd7dfcb7c08a029488c","tid":687043,"uid":13303,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T01:09:58.000Z","msg":"辣殺泛民阻住哂<br />\n呢次我撐保蝗黨"},{"pid":"1ddad6ab40953b6ed79bc44595003f09bf8c025d","tid":687043,"uid":14918,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T01:09:59.000Z","msg":"公民黨=食屎狗<br />\n<br />\n高鐵 MTR 又唔見你咁多野講"},{"pid":"9b9773f1ab8a4a999ae493eb437dc6a9f2a3d56e","tid":687043,"uid":71591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T01:10:00.000Z","msg":"跟本要audition攞牌表演"},{"pid":"dc48b181a4635cb5d48a724a3a28ee66495a40a9","tid":687043,"uid":87780,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T01:10:22.000Z","msg":"你估啲支那人唔識點玩盡個制度拎著數？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n汁柒咗佢好唔好"},{"pid":"629a986d37554c6a8fae9109108a00436ed4eb7d","tid":687043,"uid":24104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T01:10:27.000Z","msg":"表咩演呀，咪又係免費有個地方俾班冚家剷搵錢<br />\n<br />\n本身都有人管㗎，黑社會呀嘛"},{"pid":"544d34617d47e0ab2dee4e5f74ac4542128fa1f0","tid":687043,"uid":67468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T01:12:12.000Z","msg":"一念起個班老妖好想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a73dc13ee0f7e0f7ce71f9d670334432e9edeb"